latestPosts.caption:
✨ We’re delighted to share that @jewelsbyshweta will be showcasing at the Singapore International Jewelry Expo (SIJE) 2025 – Asia’s premier destination for exceptional fine jewelry and timepieces.

📍 Sands Expo & Convention Centre, Singapore
📅 10th – 13th July 2025
🔸 Hall A, B & C — Level 1

Come experience our curated selection of one-of-a-kind pieces, including rare handcrafted jewels and fresh gemstone designs — all thoughtfully presented in the heart of Singapore’s design and luxury hub.

To schedule a meeting or viewing, feel free to drop us a message here or connect via jewelsbyshweta.com.
Looking forward to seeing familiar faces and making new connections!

latestPosts.caption:
🚨 We’re Hiring in Jaipur — and open to remote collaborations too! 🚨
	1.	Shopify Website Designers & Developers
We’re looking for individuals or agencies with:
– Strong experience with Shopify theme customization & app integration
– Understanding of UI/UX design principles
– Ability to handle product uploads, checkout flows, and SEO basics
– A good sense of aesthetics, especially in the luxury design space
– Bonus: Experience with liquid code and Shopify APIs
	2.	Freelance Graphic Designers
Ideal collaborators will have:
– A strong portfolio across branding, packaging, digital media
– Proficiency in Adobe Suite (Illustrator, Photoshop, InDesign)
– An eye for luxury design sensibilities and detail
– Comfort with working in short sprints and adapting to creative briefs
– Bonus: Animation or motion design skills

We’re based in Jaipur, but also open to working with talented creatives remotely.

📩 Send your portfolios to: Jeyporecreationsusa@gmail.com

Let’s build something beautiful together.

#Hiring #GraphicDesign #ShopifyDeveloper #DesignJobs #CreativeCareers #RemoteJobs #JaipurDesign #LuxuryBrand #FreelanceDesign #ShopifyDesign #WeAreHiring
